 arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sc8280xp-crd.dts     |  6 +-
 .../qcom/sc8280xp-lenovo-thinkpad-x13s.dts    | 30 ++++-----
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sc8280xp-pmics.dtsi  | 67 ++-----------------
 4 files changed, 31 insertions(+), 81 deletions(-)

