> function and used for every case.

We refer to the functions as func() (mind the parentheses).

...

> +       ret = spi_sync_transfer(st->us, xfer, ARRAY_SIZE(xfer));
> +       if (ret) {
> +               dev_err(&st->us->dev, "problem reading register\n");

> +               return ret;
